imageDescription: A homeless person, sitting on a sidewalk with their head in their hands. They are wearing torn clothes and have a ragged beard. In front of them is a cardboard sign that says, "Sorry, I ain't got no money." The background is a busy city street, with people walking by and cars driving past.
